rows.label: tlk42450251_11_msg00001
rows.name: Waaaah! Rex! It good to see you!

rows.label: tlk42450251_11_msg00002
rows.name:
Periperi just whiling away time,
watching ships go by till cargo
all loaded on board.

rows.label: tlk42450251_11_msg00003
rows.name:
What Rex say to meal together?
Nice tasty Samod or somesuch?

rows.label: tlk42450251_11_msg00004
rows.name: Sorry... I'm kind of busy at the moment.

rows.label: tlk42450251_11_msg00006
rows.name:
Periperi thought, would be nice to
make happy memories before set
out on long, long voyage...

rows.label: tlk42450251_11_msg00007
rows.name:
Ah, never mind Periperi. Is just being
melodramatic. Rex keep up doing
good work with salvaging!
